   "sheet": "Anode Mix",
   "orientation": "landscape"
  },
  {
   "kind": "heading",
   "level": 2,
   "text": "Cleaning and Maintenance"
  },
  {
   "kind": "bullets",
   "items": [
    "Cleaning: Clean the mixer and other reusables (between 2-3 operators it will take about 3-4 hour to complete). Fill the main mixer with water until dispersion blade is submerged and stir for 0.5-2 hours with moderate heating (30-40\u00b0C? let the vapor clean the mixer ceiling). Remove the dispenser valve for cleaning. Water wipe then acetone to dry.",
    "Maintenance: Yearly maintenance is recommended to change dispersion rotor bearing and motor belt."
   ]
  },
